name: Amber Waves
description: The process for making this image was extensive. First, I used a GAN to generate an image based on the human heart. I then did a style transfer of it using another piece I did as the style. I then opened that file in Audacity and created several different data-bent versions of the image. I brought all of these into photoshop and layered them with various blending modes. Added a custom LUT and photo filter for an amber CRT vibe.
